# ── Local-only tools — NEVER deploy these ───────────────────────────────────
# Anything in _local/ is an internal tool (e.g. the Content Studio /
# _local/curator.html) that must stay off the live site. Git refuses to track
# it, so it can't be pushed to GitHub or deployed by Netlify even by accident.
_local/
